Features
--------

  - Create Ask results
  - Score
  - Streak
  - History list
  - Persist Asks


Events
------

onAppStart:
pipe(
  loadAsks,
  updateState
)

onFormSubmit:
pipe(
  createAsk,
  updateDB,
  updateState,
  clearForm,
)

onTabClick:
pipe(
  updateState
)


View
----

onStateChange:
pipe(
  updateScore,
  updateStreak,
  updateHistoryList,
  displayTab
)


App State
---------
currentTab: 'form' | 'history'
asks: [
  { timestamp: integer, ask: string, askee: string },
]
